    <h3>EHDSHealthProfessional → PractitionerEuCore</h3>
    <p class="lead">
      This page describes the element-by-element mapping from the <a href="https://www.xt-ehr.eu/fhir/models/StructureDefinition/EHDSHealthProfessional"><strong>EHDSHealthProfessional</strong></a> logical model to the <a href="StructureDefinition-practitioner-eu-core.html"><strong>PractitionerEuCore</strong></a> FHIR profile.
    </p>
    <div class="legend">
      <strong>Relationship legend</strong>
      <dl>
        <dt>equal</dt><dd>Semantically equivalent.</dd>
        <dt>narrower</dt><dd>FHIR is more specific / more constrained.</dd>
        <dt>relatedto</dt><dd>Conceptually aligned but requires interpretation or depends on context.</dd>
        <dt>unmatched</dt><dd>No direct equivalent in this FHIR profile/datatype.</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
